1 shall coordinate with one another to ensure they appoint members from a variety of backgrounds and
2 geographic areas.
3 (c) The director of the department of commerce or the director's designee shall serve as a
4 nonvoting ex officio member of the board.
5 (7) In consultation with the board, the department of commerce:
6 (a) may adopt rules to implement this section; and
7 (b) shall develop a plan to promote and solicit contributions to the Montana hunters' and anglers'
8 community fund.
